latestPosts.caption:
I didn't plan on recording such a sensitive moment in the spirit that would only be in secret but God had other plans to minister 
………
When i first started doing hair I thought it was just to make Women feel and look beautiful and when our salon “ All Numbered “ was minister to me to be the name of the salon that is when  Luke 12:7
“But even the very hairs of your head are all numbered. Fear not therefore: ye are of more value than many sparrows” made sense 

I know a lot of the “whys” the “pain” the “trails” the “lessons” the “messages” was all to understand women, in a deeper way, in a way that I can, not only hear them out, but truly understand them.
So when you ask yourself “ why me ?” There is a purpose through your pain and trial and it will be greater then your own understanding 

Just know when you have an appointment with me it’s also with God 🤍

Over 1 million entries this year 2023!!! From over 120 countries around the whole World for several Categories 
And YA GURL @jesseniaspallet Got nominated as first place for Natural Texture category 🥹🥹🥹🥹

I’m so so HONORED 😭😭😭😭

Honestly, seeing so many amazing artist I would have never thought I would get nominated because there is so many talent artists out there!!! So this is for all of us that just love to do what we do with love, passion and grace 🫶🏼🫶🏽🫶🏾🫶🏿

I wouldn’t have gotten this without all my supporters and those that see what they see in my work, those that voted and just the love is real 🥲🥲🥲

Shout out to my sister @pure.golden  who trusted me to color her hair !! And transform her look, and the amazing makeup artist that make the look come together @myaaelizaa 

God rewards his children in ways we may not expect ✨
